SUGGESTIONS 5

1. Consistency should be encouraged when entering data.

2. Some sports are only played by specific gender (e.g football). Future studies should consider studying the different sports separately.

3. The salary ratio is extremely high. Administrators should review their salary pay criteria and work on revising the salaries to promote equity.
